  "description": "From the manufacturer Deadfast Fly Window Trap The DeadfastFly Window Trap effectively attracts and traps flies, whilst keeping them out of sight. The chemical-free, scented lure entices flies inside to protect living spaces. With its decorative design, the trap offers discreet control all around the home. Chemical-free lure Flies hidden inside No residue Decorative design for discreet control Safe for use around children and pets For use indoors 4 traps How to use Step 1 Peel the film from the tab on the back of the Window Fly Trap to prepare for placement. Gently place the trap into the bottom or the top corner of a window where flies are most active Once full, pull the trap away from the window and dispose into the household bin. Advice Note: Position Window Fly Trap out of reach of pets. FOR HOW TO USE ADVICE VISIT DEADFAST.COM",
